Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:11.28,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:22.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:26.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:30.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:33.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:40.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:44.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:48.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:54.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:59.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:15.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:18.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,160.389)}The Monster Imoriges
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,690.389)}Showdown at Hell Ranch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Toru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Toru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hitomi! What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? You're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since you joined\Nthe Rider Kid Corps,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you haven't played with me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.44,0:01:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know a bunch of people have\Ngone missing in this town lately, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. My papa said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who works at the ranch goes\Nmissing and he doesn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to find out what's behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no use for women and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker kills those it has no use for!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... Michiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see what I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was a Shocker\Nmonster behind this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better contact HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better make it back\Nto the Kamen Rider Kid Corps HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:46.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an7}Kamen Rider Kid Corps\NHeadquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, a pigeon's arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll handle it.\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact number 512.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shocker monster sighted.\NCome at once. Toru."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where was 512?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,512 is Ikaho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just out, to a hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, take us with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We're members of the\NKamen Rider Kid Corps, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Mr. Taki really going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikaho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's normally an unremarkable ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But beneath it, we're\Nbuilding an airport facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet Kamen Rider has no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it's finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,we can house hundreds\Nof supersonic fighters,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:05:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,which will rain bombs down\Non cities all over Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, Japan will belong to Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Imoriges.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your ability to travel\Nwherever there's water,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring me the men I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We must complete the\Nairport as quickly as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are awfully loud in that barn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Monster!\N- You're coming with Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi! Get away, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You little brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen me, you must die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hold on tight! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi! Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could she have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This town is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster's been abducting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already had a few dozen victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've remained here to do my duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll probably leave tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did they choose this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll stop by Toru's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sure.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt, intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you dressed that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember? This is Kunisada\NChuji's birthplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out, Toru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Toru, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We got your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of monster did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:31.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,I welcome you, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.82,Italics,,0,0,0,,But you're all going to die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a Shocker monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Imoriges!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, or the child dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Imoriges!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Come to meddle again, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, take them to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... it's time you see what I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:34.48,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,He came here with the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:36.64,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:39.68,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of light,\N who sends the darkness scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:44.11,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:46.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.70,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Jump! Dive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Slam into them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:52.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Give it all you've got! Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:57.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Hit them with the force of a storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:11:01.16,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:05.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:08.77,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:23.82,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,He came here in a roar...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:26.32,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:28.47,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of lamentation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:31.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,who brings evil plots to light?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.02,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.04,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.85,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Fly! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.24,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Get the dynamo humming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.96,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Full charge! Full charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:47.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Hit them with an engine's roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:51.44,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:54.96,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:58.64,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body is going to melt away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be that easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... this isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Toru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hitomi! Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takeshi is here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, you're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't even hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, get treatment for Hitomi's wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be waiting at Hotel Tenbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:13:04.52,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, I will put an end to Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.62,Italics,,0,0,0,,Where is their home base?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:19.82,Italics,,0,0,0,,And why are they\Nkidnapping all those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.84,Italics,,0,0,0,,I don't even know what they're after...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Hitomi's injury wasn't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we get her back to the ranch?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting wrapped up in something so awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be exhausted,\Nmentally and physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back home by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I left home\Nwithout telling my big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gotta be really worried about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll walk you home, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pursue them. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency! Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki! Mr. Hongo! Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi's missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't find Toru, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're members of the Rider Kid Corps,\Nyet you let them escape your notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have anywhere\Nto go but back to the ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried. Let's follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You two stay here, in the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better take back our lost honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hitomi!\N- Big sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been? I was so worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll make valuable hostages!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I will end you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.08,Italics,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.62,Italics,,0,0,0,,If you wish to save the\Nwoman and the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:02.48,Italics,,0,0,0,,come alone to Hell Valley\Nat sunrise tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell Valley, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You came, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Hitomi and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I came alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker... where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have them working as slaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to build an airport under this ranch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,An underground airport...\NSo that's your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Return them to me, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's hot!\N- Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's hot!\N- Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Show your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Imoriges...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show no mercy this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I will not let Rider beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again... I must not be\Ndefeated by the likes of Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Screw Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.25,0:22:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.22,0:22:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, you'll see my true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki, Mitsuru. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.11,0:22:57.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The danger has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:02.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker would create a new monster\Nand attempt world domination once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:06.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ride on, our Kamen Rider... Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:10.59,Cont,,0,65,155,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:13.95,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(280.175,252.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.07,0:23:17.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I cause human bodies to melt into mud...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:21.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The sea urchin monster,\NUnidogma has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:24.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mystery of the wooden\Nbox resting in the eerie grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:30.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Stay tuned to this channel next week for "The\NTerrifying Unidogma + Ghost Monsters."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:30.84,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs105\bord0.5\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(477.167,725.389)}The Terrifying Unidogma \N+ Ghost Monsters"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.77,0:23:50.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.16,0:23:57.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:24:01.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:05.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.15,0:24:08.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.75,0:24:12.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monster Imoriges\NShowdown at Hell Ranch!